<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>微表情识人术</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: "Microsoft Yahei", sans-serif; }
        body { background: #f8f8f8; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        header { background: #222; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 40px 20px; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        header h1 { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        header p { opacity: 0.8; }
        .book-card { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 30px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); text-align: center; }
        .book-icon { font-size: 60px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .book-title { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #222; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .book-desc { font-size: 16px; color: #555; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .book-price { font-size: 26px; color: #e53935; font-weight: bold; margin: 25px 0; }
        .buy-btn { padding: 14px 40px; background: #e53935; color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 18px; cursor: pointer; }
        .buy-btn:hover { background: #c62828; }
        .section { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 25px; margin: 30px 0; }
        .section h2 { font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: #222; }
        .section p { line-height: 1.8; color: #555; margin: 8px 0; }
        footer { text-align: center; color: #999; font-size: 14px; padding: 20px 0; }

        .modal { display: none; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6); z-index: 9999; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
        .modal-content { background: #fff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 16px; max-width: 320px; width: 90%; text-align: center; }
        #qrcodeImg { width: 220px; height: 220px; display: block; margin: 15px auto; border-radius: 8px; }
        .close-btn { margin-top: 15px; padding: 10px 30px; background: #eee; border: none; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>微表情识人术</h1>
            <p>读懂微表情，一眼看穿人心、想法与真实意图</p >
        </header>

        <div class="book-card">
            <div class="book-icon">👁️</div>
            <h2 class="book-title">微表情识人看透人心全集</h2>
            <p class="book-desc">
                从面部微表情、眼神、肢体动作、说话语气<br>
                快速看穿他人内心想法、真实意愿、隐藏心思<br>
                人际交往、识人用人、避开套路必备
            </p >
            <div class="book-price">限时仅售 ¥9.90</div>
            <button class="buy-btn" onclick="openQR()">立即获取</button>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>📖 内容简介</h2>
            <p>✅ 通过微表情，判断对方是真心还是假意</p >
            <p>✅ 从眼神动作，看懂别人没说出口的心里话</p >
            <p>✅ 看穿套路、防备小人、看懂人情世故</p >
            <p>✅ 职场、交友、恋爱、做生意都能用</p >
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>❓ 购买须知</h2>
            <p>支付截图发送至邮箱：468404681@qq.com</p >
            <p>几分钟内发送完整电子版 PDF</p >
            <p>一次购买，永久随时翻看</p >
        </div>

        <footer>
            © 2026 精品电子书合集
        </footer>
    </div>

    <div id="qrModal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <h3>扫码支付 ¥9.90</h3>
            <p>微信 / 支付宝 均可扫码</p >
            < img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/longjieqimingmedia/longjieqimingmedia.github.io/main/WechatIMG71.jpg" alt="收款二维码" id="qrcodeImg">
            <p style="font-size:13px;color:#666;">付款截图发邮箱，即刻发完整资料</p >
            <button class="close-btn" onclick="closeQR()">关闭</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function openQR() {
            document.getElementById('qrModal').style.display = 'flex';
        }
        function closeQR() {
            document.getElementById('qrModal').style.display = 'none';
        }
        window.onclick = function(e){
            let m = document.getElementById('qrModal');
            if(e.target === m) m.style.display = 'none';
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
